Step 1 - Definition of Visual filter.
In this filter which is directly applied on individual visualization also within a visualization, 
the filters are applied both on data and the calculations which are used in the visualization.

Step 2 - What output we are expecting?
We want to see the Country wise sales, profit and unit sold.

Step 3 - Drag and drop the columns
Drag and drop the Sales, profit, unit sold, and country onto the task window.

Step 4 - Apply filter.
Drag and drop columns into the filters pane as per requirement, for now, we are going to use the Month name column and going to apply the filter accordingly.
